{"declarations":[{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Linter/CheckUnivs.html#Lean.Linter.CheckUnivs.checkUnivsLinter\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Linter</span>.<span class=\"name\">CheckUnivs</span>.<span class=\"name\">checkUnivsLinter</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Command.html#Lean.Elab.Command.Linter\">Linter</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Enables the `checkUnivs` linter, which warns when a declaration has a universe parameter\nthat only ever occurs in a `max u v` together with another parameter, never on its own.\nThis usually means that the type contains a `max u v` where neither `u` nor `v` occur by\nthemselves; the fix is to provide the universe level explicitly.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Linter/CheckUnivs.html#Lean.Linter.CheckUnivs.checkUnivsLinter","kind":"def","line":70,"name":"Lean.Linter.CheckUnivs.checkUnivsLinter","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Linter/CheckUnivs.lean#L70-L87"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">opaque</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Linter/CheckUnivs.html#Lean.Linter.linter.checkUnivs\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Linter</span>.<span class=\"name\">linter</span>.<span class=\"name\">checkUnivs</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Data/Options.html#Lean.Option\">Lean.Option</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Enables the `checkUnivs` linter, which warns when a declaration has a universe parameter\nthat only ever occurs in a `max u v` together with another parameter, never on its own.\nThis usually means that the type contains a `max u v` where neither `u` nor `v` occur by\nthemselves; the fix is to provide the universe level explicitly.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Linter/CheckUnivs.html#Lean.Linter.linter.checkUnivs","kind":"opaque","line":23,"name":"Lean.Linter.linter.checkUnivs","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Linter/CheckUnivs.lean#L23-L34"}}],"imports":["Lean.Linter.Basic","Lean.Linter.Util","Lean.Util.CollectLevelParams","Lean.Util.ForEachExpr"],"instances":[],"name":"Lean.Linter.CheckUnivs"}